commitResults.messageBody:
It is to fix bug as the edit, deassign operation depends on the index
given by user and also on the sorted home visit and unavailable date
list. Hence, if the display list is not sorted, then the user might
give index that does not corresponds to what they intend to change.

Hence, this is a bug that need to be fixed.

commitResults.messageBody:
The current address book does not allow the user to mark patients as
having been visited by a nurse.

Marking patients as visited will allow the user to keep track of which
patients have yet to be visited by a nurse.

Let's
- Allow the Parser to recognise "mark" as a command.
- Allow Patient class to keep track of visited status.
